# exa-answer environment template
#
# Copy this file to `.env` in this directory and fill in the required key,
# OR pass the same value via the MCP `env` block in your `~/.claude.json`.
#
# Required:
#   EXA_API_KEY — Exa API key (the same key works for the main `exa` MCP)
#
# Get a key at: https://exa.ai
# Free trial credits available at signup; PAYG pricing after.

EXA_API_KEY=your-exa-api-key-placeholder
